    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Supports of various design for the baptismal font, particularly for basin-style fonts. Examples include tabletop supports and metal supports mounted on a wall or other church architecture. For holders of baptismal fonts that rest on the floor, use "baptismal font stands."</Note_Text>
